item.title: Holding New Domain
item.description: New domain name? Why this domain? Actually one of my customers bought this domain and then asked me to setup a website for him. I created a beautiful website for him and then I was told that he lacks money. So now I own this domain and I’m offering to sell it for a good price. So in case you’re interested in this domain, just contact me at my email: abdullah@abdullah.
